{
  "stem": "20848.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And my mother-- of course, we didn't know what was going to happen to us-- so my mother has this wonderful idea.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "She took dirty sauce pans and made such a mess of our apartment.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I can't even tell you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "She put everything on top of the furniture.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And when the German SS came in to see what they can take, they had one look at the place and they said in German, [SPEAKING GERMAN], which means this is filthy.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And they walked out, so actually they didn't take anything from our flat, but it didn't do much good, because we left everything when we went to Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was-- well, I couldn't-- I wouldn't call it an apartment.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was one room with a little kitchenette.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was so cold, I can't even tell you.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was no heating there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And at that time in Warsaw, we still live in Polish area.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was no-- ghetto was not created then.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that was the first time I came across anti-Semitism from Poles, because you see, I was a little girl, and I played on the courtyard.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the Polish boys-- because it was winter it was full of snow-- they used to put stones in the snow, make snowballs out of snow and throw it at us, at Jewish children, and used to scream you-- you-- what would amount to bloody Jews, you know.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they were very, very anti-Semitic.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the place was, I would say, pretty depressing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And it was so cold that I developed chilblains, and so did my brother.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We had chilblains on our toes and our hands.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I remember my father used to put newspaper and, I think it was petroleum or whatever, which is to help.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
